  "slug": "dream-bars-toffee-coconut",
  "title": "Dream bars",
  "subtitle": "Shortbread base with a toffee coconut and walnut topping",
  "excerpt": "A two-layer traybake: a buttery shortbread base pressed into the tin and par-baked, then covered with a sticky toffee topping made from eggs, golden syrup, and desiccated coconut before going back into the oven until set and caramelised. The bottom layer provides the crisp, buttery contrast to the chewy, sweet top. Cut into small bars once completely cool; they keep for several days in an airtight tin.",
